data.description: Welcome to the home you've been searching for in the highly sought-after Victoria Park! This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers the perfect combination of beauty, comfort, and serenity.  As you enter, you'll be greeted by the spacious, cozy open floor plan that seamlessly connects the kitchen, coffee/Tea station, dining room, and living room. If you peek to your left on your way in, you'll notice the office which can easily be converted to a playroom, homeschooling area or whatever pleases your heart. The kitchen features a gas range and oven, stainless steel appliances, a stone counter convenient breakfast bar, and a spacious walk-in pantry, making it a hub for everyday living and entertaining.  The entire living space is adorned with stylish and low-maintenance tile floors, ensuring a seamless look and easy cleaning. If you prefer the outdoors, escape through the glass sliding doors and enter the tranquility of the backyard, featuring privacy roll down shade, inground heated pool and spa.  The screened porch and fully fenced yard gives you plenty of privacy. There's also low maintenance synthetic grass turf, and mature shrubs lining the back yard for an added layer of privacy and beauty.  Wonderful place to rejuvenate, unwind or entertain your guests.   The primary bedroom offers ample space for a king-sized bed and furniture, suite bathroom featuring two separate sinks, a soaking tub, separate shower and a large walk-in closet. This home features lots of upgrades, smart technology controls pool lights, features, and thermostat all from your smart phone!  The two-car garage is equipped with quality ceiling storage rack system that conveys.    The location is less than 2 miles to I-4, offering an easy commute to Orlando theme Parks or the beaches. Nestled nearby retail shops, grocery stores, restaurants’, and medical care facilities. As part of the Victoria Park community, you'll enjoy wonderful HOA amenities, internet and cable provider, a community pool, sidewalks throughout for a stroll, community events planner, playgrounds, and a fitness gym. Call to schedule your appointment to view this fantastic home in a very desirable community!
